CASE 1 Stoichiometric Hydrogen Air Case
UDET  1.6738E+05! CJ detonation velocity 
T1 293.0! initial temperature (preshock)
P1 1.0! initial pressure (preshock)
REAC  
N2  0.73591
O2  0.19562
CH4 0.06847
END
ATOL  1.E-9 ! absolute tolerance
RTOL  1.E-10 ! relative tolerance
PLOT  1    !prints out plot output every 10th solver step
END
STOP
